query:
SELECT
                rgd.gateway_id_bs58,
                derived_aes256_gcm_siv_key,
                gateway_listener,
                fallback_listener
            FROM
                remote_gateway_details AS rgd
            INNER JOIN
                remote_gateway_shared_keys AS rgsk
            ON
                rgd.gateway_id_bs58 = rgsk.gateway_id_bs58
            WHERE
                rgd.gateway_id_bs58 = ?
